      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Off Your Rocker",
        "Client": "Lava Caverns Excavator",
        "Description": "Dude... I\u0027m freaking out. Every\r\ntime I go to the Lava Caverns,\r\nI keep hearing this creepy voice.\r\nLike, I look around, and no one\r\nis there! No one! Uh, can you go\r\nand check it out for me? I know\r\nI\u0027m not crazy!",
